#agadmator Link to article https://www.chess.com/article/view/the-strongest-player-you-ve-never-heard-of 

Salomon Flohr vs Rudolf Pitschak
**Rd--()-, Bilin (1930) 
Indian Game: Knights Variation. General (A46)
